## Code Standards

| Principle | Requirement |
|-----------|-------------|
| **TDD** | Write tests BEFORE implementation |
| **DRY** | 3+ identical blocks → extract to function |
| **Types** | Annotations required, proper None handling |
| **Files** | <500 lines per file |
| **Security** | No secrets in logs |

